Build forky-gnome sdcard for tinkerboard 3:

Input files: ../rootfs-forky/linaro-rootfs.img
                            /linaro-esp.img

Plugin usb3 stick to PC.
sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
Eject usb3 stick from PC.

Plugin usb3 stick to tinkerboard 3.
Login:
Username: linaro
Password: linaro
Setup wifi.
Disable power saving, auto suspend and screen saver.
uname -a
lsb_release -a
sudo dpkg-reconfigure tzdata
sudo dpkg-reconfigure locales
date
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade
sync
free
glxinfo | grep OpenGL
date
Check if Debian is running UEFI mode:
ls /sys/firmware/efi
Check display mode: ( wayland or x11 )
echo $XDG_SESSION_TYPE
Check audio driver: ( pulseaudio or pipewire )
pactl info

sudo apt install speedtest-cli python3-pip python3-setuptools ffmpeg mpv glmark2-es2-wayland pandoc firefox-esr vlc vlc-plugin-video-output pavucontrol rfkill vsftpd

speedtest-cli --secure

glmark2-es2-wayland

aplay -l
pavucontrol  ( select hdmi0 as default )

firefox -> youtube.com -> search YmDNhi07_Ho

Do follows on PC, then ftp swan.mp4 to tinkerboard 3.
(
git clone https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp.git
cd yt-dlp
make
cd ../
~/yt-dlp/yt-dlp -f 'bestvideo[ext=mp4]+bestaudio[ext=m4a]' 3qrKjywjo7Q -o swan.mp4 --postprocessor-args " -c:v libx265 -b:v 2M -c:a copy"
)

mpv --hwdec=auto-copy swan.mp4
ffplay swan.mp4
cvlc --gl=wgl --glconv=any swan.mp4

sudo rfkill list
hciconfig hci0
hcitool dev
hciconfig -a
